	\n\nAddress: 122 128th St SE\, Everett\, WA 98208\n\nPlease join your fell
	ow Mill Creek Chamber members and guests to our monthly member-hosted even
	t where businesses get to network\, learn about each other\, and connect o
	n a personal and casual level! Guests welcome also!\n\nAlways an exciting 
	new Mill Creek Chamber event\; we’ll be hosted at new location each month\
	, so if you have a venue that you’d like to gain more exposure from\, plea
	se let us know!\n\nIf you’re a guest\, we welcome you to learn more about 
	the benefits of membership. When available\, our Chamber Director will be 
	present to discuss\, and when not\; Networking Committee members can assis
	t as well.\n\nHave some coffee\, make some connections.\n\n• March 10th\, 
	2026\n\n• 8am-9:30am\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/coff
	ee-connections-march/18282542/2026-03-10T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drin
	k
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/coffee-connections-march/
	18282542/2026-03-10T00
LOCATION:Active Mill Creek\, 122 128th St SE\, Everett\, WA
